Title: 157: The Amazing World of a Data Science Meetup
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Meetup organizer and enthusiast, Mary Loubele. You will learn how to organize your first Meetup group, ways to encourage people in Meetups to interact with each other, and you will learn about the current state of deep learning and NLP.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/157
